Woot watcher is a trival woot screen scrapper that polls the site every 5 minutes, parses it with Hpricot, and growls new items it finds.  Could be modified with little difficulty to poll Ebay etc.  Please be kind and do not lower the poll rate to respect Woot's bandwidth.

